{"tid":1264454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 既然已經割咗... 點先可以令港共驚？","createTime":"2019-06-28T16:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T17:39:57.000Z","uid":267268,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e8ea564bc6a306b69d098240512069dc7f939e","tid":1264454,"uid":267268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"唔知有無巴打發過類似嘅夢，啱啱發夢責醒咗：<br />\n<br />\n夢入面我屋企比人霸咗，屋企人係屋企周圍叫人還返間屋比我地<br />\n<br />\n不過我就好似行行下行咗去惡霸屋企嘈，嘈到佢啲鄰居都怕怕，仲要整埋花牌比佢地，唔放人樣，你知呢啲老一輩都唔鐘意呢啲野架嘛，直頭嚇撚死佢地啦<br />\n<br />\n話說出賣我屋企嘅人梗係唔止一個啦，輪流去佢地屋企理論講解我擁有我屋企主權，有時仲嘈到佢地啲鄰居頂唔順，鄙視佢地添<br />\n<br />\n其實真係要咁做啲惡霸先識驚架<br />\n<br />\n唔會即時有效嘅，不過都好大壓力架。"},{"pid":"05cf948465b4c85e0959e7a65422133e506cc03c","tid":1264454,"uid":267268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:57:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec7fd1fe9fb12fc097437acb82d7732743db7799","tid":1264454,"uid":267268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1e4f090298adeeb34f607fa89f10202a9bba17ac","tid":1264454,"uid":267268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:34:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1a83fcc4de9c1967e7ea59bc3b634d2e6e08abd8","tid":1264454,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:35:11.000Z","msg":"七月十四燒街衣，是否屬基本法保障原有生活方式五十年不變保障？"},{"pid":"33ac716dfa856b472bf58927b5201036965f4497","tid":1264454,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"有冇聽過核災"},{"pid":"b25e51211376ba6a5e8317932a8bebc998f78db3","tid":1264454,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:36:09.000Z","msg":"再世諸葛亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc7bd2